Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@jewelcart.com",
  "password": "Admin@123",
  "firstName": "Admin",
  "lastName": "User"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@jewelcart.com",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

